      "fieldName": "DAY LIMIT FOR RESTART",
      "dataType": "NUMERIC",
      "rawType": "NJ3,0",
      "length": 3,
      "required": false,
      "helpText": "This field will reflect the value for the maximum number of days that may elapse between an interuption of this instrument and the restart of this  instrument.  This value, in days, will be used for this instrument ONLY and override the value in the Mental Health Site file.   Note that in both fields the day limit is inclusive, so that as long as the elapsed days do not exceed this value then the instrument may be  restarted. ",
